Arbitrary Precision Mathematics Library



BUILDING:
---------

	cd arbprec
	make 


TESTING:
--------

	Run the test binary:

		./tests/test-arbitrary-precision number number base scale

	Run the algorithm D division test suite:

		make test


USING THE API:
--------------

	Look inside of the various tests inside of tests/ for examples on how
	to use the API.


NOTES ON COPYING:
----------------

	This project is MIT licensed as per the current trends. Hoewever, this
	is not an invitation to other developers to take ideas and code without
	attribution! Please be ethical. If there is code here that you would
	like to use -- pay proper attribution.


